                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#43r"/>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአባ፡ ተወልደ፡ መድኅን፡ ወልደ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ዘገዳመ፡ ዋሊ፡ ዘሴጣ፡ ወዘተአገላ፡ አምኀሉ፡ ነጋድያን፡ ኢይትዓ
                           </q>
                           <note>
                              The note is incomplete. It states that ʾAbbā <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11351TawaldaM">Tawalda Madḫǝn</persName>,
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11232HouseSam">spiritual son of Sāmuʾel of Gadāma Wāli</persName>, is the owner of the book.
                           </note>
